    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Henosepilachna implicata (Mulsant): a) female, dorsal view; b) male, dorsal view; c) abdomen, male; d) abdomen, female; e) abdominal postcoxal line; f–i) male genitalia: f) tegmen, lateral view; g) tegmen, ventral view; h) penis; i) penis apex; j) female genitalia: coxites." ;
