    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Henosepilachna circularis (Korschefsky): a) male, dorsal view; b) male, lateral view; c) abdominal postcoxal line; d–g) male genitalia: d) tegmen, ventral view; e) tegmen, lateral view; f) penis; g) penis apex; h–o) variations in the male genita- lia of H. implicata (collected from Trichy, Tamil Nadu): h–l) penis guide in lateral view; m–o) penis capsule." ;
